#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.149"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.149:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.149:0.2"
msgid "12. Balakaraṇīyavagga"
msgstr "12. Hard Work"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.149:0.3"
msgid "149. Balasutta"
msgstr "149. Hard Work"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.46"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.149:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn45.149:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ye keci balakaraṇīyā kammantā karīyanti, sabbe te "
"pathaviṃ nissāya pathaviyaṃ patiṭṭhāya evamete balakaraṇīyā kammantā "
"karīyanti;"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, all the hard work that gets done depends on the earth and is "
"grounded on the earth."

msgctxt "sn45.149:1.3"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, a mendicant develops and cultivates the noble eightfold "
"path depending on and grounded on ethics."

msgctxt "sn45.149:1.4"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti?"
msgstr ""
"And how does a mendicant grounded on ethics develop and cultivate the noble "
"eightfold path?"

msgctxt "sn45.149:1.5"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ "
"nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops right view, right thought, right speech, "
"right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right "
"immersion, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen as "
"letting go."

msgctxt "sn45.149:1.6"
msgid ""
"evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarotīti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how a mendicant grounded on ethics develops and cultivates the noble "
"eightfold path.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.149:2.1"
msgid "(Paragaṅgāpeyyālīvaṇṇiyato paripuṇṇasuttanti vitthāramaggī.)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.149:3.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ye keci balakaraṇīyā kammantā karīyanti, sabbe te "
"pathaviṃ nissāya pathaviyaṃ patiṭṭhāya evamete balakaraṇīyā kammantā "
"karīyanti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.149:3.2"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.149:3.3"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.149:3.4"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti rāgavinayapariyosānaṃ "
"dosavinayapariyosānaṃ mohavinayapariyosānaṃ … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti "
"rāgavinayapariyosānaṃ dosavinayapariyosānaṃ mohavinayapariyosānaṃ."
msgstr "“… which culminate in the removal of greed, hate, and delusion …”"

msgctxt "sn45.149:3.5"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarotīti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.149:4.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ye keci balakaraṇīyā kammantā karīyanti, sabbe te "
"pathaviṃ nissāya pathaviyaṃ patiṭṭhāya evamete balakaraṇīyā kammantā "
"karīyanti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.149:4.2"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.149:4.3"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.149:4.4"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti amatogadhaṃ amataparāyanaṃ "
"amatapariyosānaṃ … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti amatogadhaṃ amataparāyanaṃ "
"amatapariyosānaṃ."
msgstr "“… culminate, finish, and end in the deathless …”"

msgctxt "sn45.149:4.5"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarotīti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.149:5.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ye keci balakaraṇīyā kammantā karīyanti, sabbe te "
"pathaviṃ nissāya pathaviyaṃ patiṭṭhāya evamete balakaraṇīyā kammantā "
"karīyanti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.149:5.2"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.149:5.3"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.149:5.4"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti nibbānaninnaṃ nibbānapoṇaṃ "
"nibbānapabbhāraṃ … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti nibbānaninnaṃ nibbānapoṇaṃ "
"nibbānapabbhāraṃ."
msgstr "“… slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment …”"

msgctxt "sn45.149:5.5"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarotī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.149:5.6"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
